{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"62e23ffa35","title":"军委关于同意西北部署的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"93380d6e66","index":0,"year":1953,"month":3,"day":10,"articleId":"62e23ffa35"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"10700d436f","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"62e23ffa35","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会起草的给中国人民解放军西北军区并西南军区的电报。"},{"id":"c24a2c7971","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"62e23ffa35","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中国人民解放军西北军区于1952年11月成立的甘青剩汇指挥部，彭绍辉任司令员，廖汉生任政治委员，负责指挥所属部队，在西南军区和空军配合下，剩灭盘据甘（肃）、青（海）、（四）川边藏族居住地区的马良武装股。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ad02b1a030","type":"title","text":"军委关于同意西北潮菲部署的电报”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"62e23ffa35"},{"id":"10700d436f","type":"paragraph","text":"西北军区，并西南军区","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"62e23ffa35"},{"id":"c24a2c7971","type":"paragraph","text":"西北军区三月八日电蒸。同意甘青期指之期能部署及西北军区之意见。望令期指注意可能遇到的各种困难，主要是物质补给困难和少数民族对我不了解的困难，遇到这些困难时，必须鼓励部属想尽一切办法克服之，务达全歼各，不可半途而废。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"62e23ffa35"},{"id":"cd5606534a","type":"subtitle","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"62e23ffa35"},{"id":"11386a5789","type":"paragraph","text":"三月十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"62e23ffa35"}],"page":{"id":"f007ec8aab","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"62e23ffa35","start":64,"end":64}}}},"__N_SSG":true}